  <acronym>HiTS</acronym>
  <official_title>A Prospective Proof of Concept Study to Evaluate the Potential Efficacy of Ustekinumab in Patients With Moderate to Severe Hidradenitis Suppurativa (Acne Ectopica)</official_title>
