  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to determine whether ustekinumab is effective in the treatment
      of moderate to severe hidradenitis suppurativa.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      An open label prospective study is performed to investigate the effectiveness and safety of
      ustekinumab in hidradenitis suppurativa. Twenty patients will be included. They will receive
      ustekinumab 45 or 90 mg on weeks 0-4-16-28. Patients will be followed up untill week 40.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
